{"tid":207150,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣香港U canteen 大比拼","createTime":"2017-04-18T19:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T09:56:29.000Z","uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0aace42228e49e99ecab6a494d75ffd73baa5276","tid":207150,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T19:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知有冇人肯睇"},{"pid":"b557a38f95c6fa2739ebb22efac2976a9c5341a0","tid":207150,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T19:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h1gqn0y2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh1gqn0y2&h=b02b636f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先貼一張之前影既晚餐<br />\n滷水雞肶鮮嫩 多汁<br />\n椰菜 台灣叫高麗菜<br />\n通常加d蒜就炒 食落爽口<br />\n60台幣一餐 包湯 野飲任拎 有紅茶綠茶"},{"pid":"7a626850076bb66659371815ecdebde4e2eb816d","tid":207150,"uid":69626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T19:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/h1gqn0y2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh1gqn0y2&h=b02b636f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先貼一張之前影既晚餐<br />\n滷水雞肶鮮嫩 多汁<br />\n椰菜 台灣叫高麗菜<br />\n通常加d蒜就炒 食落爽口<br />\n60台幣一餐 包湯 野飲任拎 有紅茶綠茶</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好肚餓"},{"pid":"40a06d8f8a52eb213fc16c463c1e1af3574c8d1e","tid":207150,"uid":86423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T20:03:45.000Z","msg":"台灣U canteen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c44decce9fdd0bbb8fb91f61de617de48c1f751","tid":207150,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"準備食午餐  食乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3395f921a8cf9da46bcb360e48b41fa46d70e595","tid":207150,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"得一張相比乜拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fd19e6ea8821f44ca7d193f79138cbd75c47b7","tid":207150,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"唔駛比啦, 慳返 D 時間<br />\n<br />\n班 on 9 仔實諗到 D 藉口話香港贏哂"},{"pid":"73136fd3976355b84032c72b98660f832cbea46c","tid":207150,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/h1gqn0y2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh1gqn0y2&h=b02b636f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先貼一張之前影既晚餐<br />\n滷水雞肶鮮嫩 多汁<br />\n椰菜 台灣叫高麗菜<br />\n通常加d蒜就炒 食落爽口<br />\n60台幣一餐 包湯 野飲任拎 有紅茶綠茶</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好肚餓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD 菜狗都唔屌,一係超油(油浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ),好臭 OR 凍既<br />\n我自己烚分分鐘仲好食<br />\n<br />\n飯就勁濕勁淋,你鐘意呢種口感既無野好講,我就唔好呢種飯粒<br />\n<br />\n唯一雞係唔錯,台灣人整雞好多都係炸,但係佢本身個肉質正過香港果堆冰鮮雞,咬落去口感肉汁都一流<br />\n當然都有好多組合肉扮雞肉,自己要小心揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132f0a8accf55106aad7c767a5b15712e288e947","tid":207150,"uid":23412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"任加飯任飲湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab8db119c4de61593aa3ce3aecd136625070960","tid":207150,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"中大NA頹飯依家幾錢"}]}